RAILS NEW PROJECT
----------------------------------------
rails new Hosital_Management -d postgres

RAILS CREATE DATABASE(config ->database.yml)
-----------------------------------------
rake db:create

RAILS CREATE TABLE
------------------------------------------
*	rails generate model patient
	rake db:migrate

RAILS ADD COLUMN
------------------------------------------
*	rails g migration add_Gender_to_patients Gender:string
	rake db:migrate

RAILS REMOVE COLUMN
-------------------------------------------
*	rails g migration remove_Gender_from_patients Gender:string
	rake db:migrate

RAILS CHANGE DATA TYPE
-------------------------------------------
*	rails g migration change_data_type_for_problem
	rake db:migrate

RAILS REMOVE COLUMN FROM DATABASE
--------------------------------------------
*	rails g migration remove_division_from_patients delete:string
	rake db:migrate

DROP TABLE IN RAILS
---------------------------------------------
*	rails g migration DropDoctors
	rake db:migrate
	